<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html class="loginPage">
<head>
    <title>Punjab Health Transparency Portal</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="./img/logo1n.png" type="image/x-icon">

    <meta name="description" content="DHIS 2">
    <meta name="keywords" content="DHIS 2">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">

    <script src="lib/js/jquerymin.js"></script>

    <script src="//dhis2-cdn.org/v221/ext/ext-all.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="lib/css/bootstrapmin.css" integrity="" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <link rel="stylesheet"  href="lib/css/bootstrapthememin.css" integrity="" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <script src="lib/js/bootstrapmin.js"  ></script>
    <script src="lib/js/bootstrapselectmin.js" ></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="lib/css/bootstrap-selectmin.css" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="lib/css/w3.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="lib/css/style.css">

    <style>
        #header{
            padding: 1em;
            color: white;
            background-color: #2978B3;
            height:auto;
            width:100%;
        }
        nav {
            float: left;
            max-width: 300px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 1em;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        nav ul a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        #test1 {
            margin-left: 120px;
            margin-right : 120px;
            padding: 1em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .noDisplay{
            display: none;
        }

        #footer{
            width: 100%;
            margin:0 auto;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0px;
            background-color: #2978B3;
        }
        h2{
            font-family: "Arial";
            font-size: 100%;
        } h1{
              font-family: "Arial";
              font-size: 250%;
          }
        p{
            font-family:  "Arial";
            font-size: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="myModal" role="dialog">
    <div class="modal-dialog">

        <!-- Modal content-->
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header" >
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                <h4><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock"></span> Login</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body" >

                <div id="loginField">
                    <div id="loginArea">
                        <div id="bannerArea">
                            <img src="" style="border:none">
                        </div>

                        <form id="loginForm" action="../../dhis-web-commons-security/login.action" method="post">
                            <div>
                                <div id="signInLabel">Sign in</div>
                                <div><input type="text" autofocus="autofocus" id="j_username" name="j_username" placeholder="Username"></div>
                                <div><input type="password" id="j_password" name="j_password" autocomplete="off" placeholder="Password"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div style="padding-bottom: 10px">
                                <a id="createAccountLink" target="_blank" href="lib/controllers/register.html">Create an account</a>
                            </div>
                            <div id="submitDiv">
                                <input id="submit" class="button" type="submit" value="Sign in">
                            </div>
                            #if( $keyAccountRecovery )
                            <div style="padding-bottom: 10px">
                                <a id="forgotPasswordLink" href="recovery.action">Forgot password?</a>
                            </div>
                            #end
                            #if( $keyConfig.selfRegistrationAllowed() )
                            <!--<div style="padding-bottom: 10px">-->
                            <!--<a id="createAccountLink" href="account.action">Create an account</a>-->
                            <!--</div>-->
                            #end
                        </form>
                        #if( $keyOpenIdProvider )
                        <form id="openIdLoginForm" action="../../dhis-web-commons-security/openid.action" method="post">
                            <input name="openid_identifier" type="hidden" value="$keyOpenIdProvider"/>
                            <div id="submitDiv">
                                #if( $keyOpenIdProviderLabel )
                                <input style="width: 269px;" id="submit" class="button" type="submit" value="$keyOpenIdProviderLabel">
                                #else
                                <input style="width: 269px;" id="submit" class="button" type="submit" value="Sign in with OpenID">
                                #end
                            </div>
                        </form>
                        #end
                        #if( $failed == true )
                        <div id="loginMessage">Wrong username or password</div>
                        #end
                        #if ( $keyApplicationNotification )
                        <div id="notificationArea">$!{keyApplicationNotification}</div>
                        #end
                        <!--[if lte IE 8]>
                        <div id="notificationArea" style="color: white; background-color: red;">$i18n.getString( "unsupported_browser" )</div>
                        <![endif]-->
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
</div>
<!--Header -->
<div id="header">
    <table>
        <tr>
            <td rowspan="2">
                <img src="img/Punjab_logo.png" width="80px">
            </td>
            <td>
                <h3 style="color:#fff">Punjab Health Facility Portal</h3>
            </td>

            <td>
                <ul style="list-style-type:none;">
                    <li class="w3-btn"><a onclick="window.location.reload()" target="_blank" style="color:#fff">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="w3-btn"><a href="http://pbhealth.gov.in/" target="_blank" style="color:#fff"> Punjab Health Department</a></li>
                    <!--<li class="w3-btn w3-hover-who1"><a href="http://www.pbhealth.gov.in/phsc.htm">Punjab DGHS</a></li>-->
                    <li class="w3-btn" id="b1" class="button12" data-toggle="modal"  style="color:#fff" data-target="#myModal"><b>Register Facility/Login</b></li>
                </ul>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>
<!--DropDown Bar-->
<div  class="w3-row " style="text-align:center; padding-top: 20px">
    <div class="w3-col w3-container" style="width:30%">
        <select id="drop1" class="selectpicker"  data-live-search="true" >
            <option value="" disabled selected hidden>Please Select State/District</option>
            <option value="wSslG6mcGXl">Select Entire State (Punjab)</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-col w3-container" style="width:30%">
        <select id="drophospital" class="selectpicker" data-live-search="true" >
            <option value="all" disabled selected hidden>Search by Hospital Name</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-col w3-container" style="width:30%">
        <select id="drop2"  class="selectpicker"  data-live-search="true">
            <option disabled selected hidden>Search by speciality</option>
        </select>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="w3-row" style="padding-top: 10px">
    <div class="w3-col w3-container" style="margin-left:170px; width:33%">
        <select id="drop_ownership"  class="selectpicker"   data-live-search="true">
            <option value="" disabled selected hidden>Search by Ownership</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-col w3-container" style="width:20%">
        <select id="droptype"  class="selectpicker"  data-live-search="true">
            <option disabled selected hidden>Type of Health Facility</option>
        </select>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="content1">
    <table>
        <tr>
            <td style="width: 500px">
                <h3 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 5%">About Us</h3>
                <p style="text-align:justify; margin-left: 50px">The Government of Punjab is pleased to announce the launch of the “Punjab Health Facility Portal” where all public and private health facilities are invited to self-report on the various health services they provide in their respective health facilities. This information will be made available to citizens through this portal to allow them to make more informed choices of what health services they can access from where. The information will help the Punjab Government to identify gaps and strengthen health services delivery and improve citizen satisfaction.
                    </br></br>We request you to partner with the State to make this important venture a resounding success. For this, healthcare providers are requested to self-register by clicking on “Register Facility/Login” button. Please note this portal will be dynamic and allow for changes to be made as they take place in future. Users of health facilities are requested to provide feedback.
                    </br></br>We hope that citizens of state find this portal useful and provide feedback regarding services.</p>
            </td>
            <td>
                <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1750772.7212624417!2d74.27996482023067!3d31.012930230614476!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x391964aa569e7355%3A0x8fbd263103a38861!2sPunjab!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1478332283034"  style="border: 0;margin-top: 5%;height: 400px;width: 500px;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;" allowfullscreen> </iframe>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

<div id="footer">
    <p style="text-align: center; color: #fff">Disclaimer: The responsibility for the correctness of data in the portal is the responsibility of the facility which has self-registered the data. The Government is only responsible for the dissemination of this information through this portal.</p>
</div>

</body>

<!-- Login Script -->
<script src="lib/scriptcontroller.js"></script>

</html>